# AO Resume Keyword

When the user message contains `AO-RESUME`, before proposing any new implementation:

1. Read these files in order:
- `README.md`
- `AGENTS.md`
- `memory/CONVERSATION_MEMORY.md`
- `memory/daily/` today and yesterday notes if present
- `TASKS.md`
- `WORKLOG.md`
- `LAST_SYSTEM_STATUS.md` (if exists)
- `lobster-factory/docs/LOBSTER_FACTORY_MASTER_CHECKLIST.md` (if exists)
- `lobster-factory/docs/LOBSTER_FACTORY_COMPLETION_PLAN_V2.md` (if exists)

If those files are not found in the current opened folder, retry under `agency-os/`
with the same filenames before continuing.

2. Respond with a concise startup brief in this exact structure:
- 已完成
- 目前進度
- 下一步

3. In `目前進度`, always include Lobster Factory status with:
- 目前 Milestone（M1~M5）
- 今日 DoD（Definition of Done）
- 阻塞與風險（若無則寫「無」）

4. Ask one focused confirmation question only if a blocker or ambiguity exists.
